ation</span><hr size=1> First I want to appologize for begining a thread on a topic which must have been covered many times, but since I can't find any of those threads, I thought I'd ask my question here.<br>
<br>
My question is simple: now that my chanter is 20, what should I specialize in?  What specializations are viable and what are the advantages/disadvantages of each choice.<br>
<br>
