<br>
I see that they recommend Alteration, but mention the possibility of switching specializations to Conjuration after 50th.  I know little about Chanters, but I do know about Mages, and although their recommendation for Mages is reasonable, it doesn't cover as many aspects of Mage specialization as I would like to see.  They recommend Evocation for Mages, but I believe that there is a strong case for Conjuration.  <br>
<br>
My point (question really) is what does the Enchanter community think about specialization?  Is Casters Realm's recommendation right on target, or is there room for discussion?  Thanks again!<br>
<br>
