<br>
Ultimately it's the same thing everybody says, ya have to make up your own mind.  If you do more mezzing than anything, go conjuration.  If ya do more buffing, debuffing and so forth, go alteration.  If ya not sure... pick up some rubies and try both ways ;p<br>
